  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\n`forge verify` accepts `retry: RetryArgs,` to configure how often to retry.\r\n\r\nthis is currently missing in `ScriptArgs`\r\n\r\n\r\n- [ ] add `retry: RetryArgs` to `ScriptArgs` (requires `verify`)\r\n- [ ] use `retry` when executing the verify command internally\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_",
